
```{=html}
<% for (const item of items) { %>

<!-- <h2><%- item.category %></h2> -->

<p><%- item.description %></p>

<div class="grid">
  <div class="grid-sizer"></div>

<% for (const tile of item.tiles) { %>
  <div class="grid-item card border-2 rounded-3 <%= tile.category %>">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title"><%= tile.title %></h4>
      <h5 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted"><%= tile.subtitle %></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
    <a href="https://packages.tesselle.org/<%= tile.title %>">
      <img src="https://www.tesselle.org/images/<%= tile.title %>.png" alt="<%= tile.title %>" class="card-img-top"/>
    </a>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <a href="https://cran.r-project.org/package=<%= tile.title %>">
        <img src="http://www.r-pkg.org/badges/version/<%= tile.title %>" alt="CRAN version" />
      </a>
      <% if (tile.status == 'active') { %>
        <a href="https://www.repostatus.org/#active">
          <img src="https://www.repostatus.org/badges/latest/active.svg" alt="Project Status: Active – The project has reached a stable, usable state and is being actively developed." />
        </a>
      <% } %>
      <% if (tile.status == 'wip') { %>
        <a href="https://www.repostatus.org/#wip">
          <img src="https://www.repostatus.org/badges/latest/wip.svg" alt="Project Status: WIP – Initial development is in progress, but there has not yet been a stable, usable release suitable for the public." />
        </a>
      <% } %>

      <p class="card-text"><%= tile.description %></p>
      <a href="https://packages.tesselle.org/<%= tile.title %>" class="card-link">Documentation</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/tesselle/<%= tile.title %>" class="card-link">Source code</a>
    </div>
  </div>
<% } %>

</div>

<% } %>
```
